Package: fdClassify
Type: Package
Title: Library of Flash Drought classificaition methods
Version: 0.4.1
Author: Pedro Alencar
Maintainer: Pedro Alencar <pedro.alencar@campus.tu-berlin.de>
Description: This package brings functions to classify FD based on several definitions from the literature:
    - Ford and Labosier (2017)
    - Pendergrass et al. (2020)
    - Noguera et al. (2020)    
    - Noguera et al. (2020)
    - Christian et al. (2020)
    - Osman et al. (2021)
        * Please refer to the README file for further bibliography of the package
